<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">###<sp/>I<sp/>would<sp/>like<sp/>to<sp/>donate</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>Time:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>Read<sp/>[contributing](CONTRIBUTING.md)<sp/>documentation.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>Fork,<sp/>clone,<sp/>hack<sp/>and<sp/>send<sp/>a<sp/>pull<sp/>request.</highlight></codeline>
